    <h4>🔐 Secure Authentication</h4>
    <p>Passwords are hashed using <code>bcrypt</code> before being stored in the SQLite database.</p>
    <pre><code>const hashed = await bcrypt.hash(password, 10);
db.run('INSERT INTO users (username, password) VALUES (?, ?)', [username, hashed]);</code></pre>

    <h4>🎨 User Interface Enhancements</h4>
    <p>Bootstrap 5 is used for responsive layout and styling, including modals, cards, and parallax backgrounds via CSS.</p>
    <pre><code>body {
  background: url('/images/background.jpg') no-repeat center center fixed;
  background-size: cover;
}</code></pre>

    <h4>📦 Session Management</h4>
    <p>Sessions are stored in SQLite with <code>connect-sqlite3</code>:</p>
    <pre><code>app.use(session({
  store: new SQLiteStore({ db: 'sessions.sqlite' }),
  secret: process.env.SESSION_SECRET,
  resave: false,
  saveUninitialized: false
}));</code></pre>

    <h4>📊 Dynamic Dashboard Content</h4>
    <p>Dashboard cards are rendered with client-side JavaScript from a local JSON array.</p>
    <pre><code>jsonData.forEach(item => {
